{"tid":325644,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"未見過咁臉皮厚嘅女子","createTime":"2017-07-17T11:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T12:07:37.000Z","uid":117747,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a79adefe431ed4c1a9e625ee741da22e7adcf9","tid":325644,"uid":117747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:20:59.000Z","msg":"話說今日收工時見落雨，就諗住揸車兜埋幾個同事出去轉車 (身處碼頭荒無區域，得獨市小巴/穿梭巴搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n同事A因為係另一邊office,所以就約咗喺大堂等。而我就同另外兩個同事B&amp;C一齊落樓攞車。<br />\n<br />\n點知有個厚臉皮女同事(下稱&ldquo;厚皮女&rdquo;)見到同事A，就問佢做乜企喺度。<br />\n咁同事A就講&ldquo;有車坐&rdquo;。呢個時候我咁岩行喺厚皮女旁邊，佢居然喺大堂一直跟住我步速去攞車，一直用眼神望住我。我寧做小人都唔想佢車佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (因為佢喺公司係屬於搬弄是非, 又巴渣果種人)。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候為免尷尬唯有加速去攞車，點知厚皮女癡埋同事A行埋去我架車問我架車有無位剩。嘩屌...我真係未見過呢種人。<br />\n去到呢個位，我真係唔知點推，er咗一陣唯有講&ldquo;有嘅...&rdquo;。 佢真係唔客氣一嘢就跳上我架車坐正個中排位。而同事A上車都識自己去車尾。 同事B&amp;C嚟到我車就猶豫咗陣，厚皮女先意識到自己坐錯位....<br />\n咁算啦，dum心口都無用，人都上咗車。<br />\n點知去到落車位，厚皮女居然&ldquo;唔該&rdquo;都無句。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想知各位巴絲有無遇過呢種不識時務嘅人？又會點樣處理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312d246a1dc6910a974c37ee1874bfe2c879bb80","tid":325644,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:24:29.000Z","msg":"直接答無位要去兜埋其他同事/朋友"},{"pid":"d7b67b7ece625d83c1108dfc2e8ebcc7449f580f","tid":325644,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:24:52.000Z","msg":"以後你都要車埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa776ebe7d4f83847680470d6de15c3f6cb11156","tid":325644,"uid":15887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"又馬後炮"},{"pid":"3402e9344c55e4ee8537f99b184e2d68aa399754","tid":325644,"uid":706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:26:36.000Z","msg":"會直接唔車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢講有其他人要兜埋<br />\n擺到明唔妥你 吹咩<br />\n除非你要車既人同佢好熟/ 你要買佢怕"},{"pid":"c868d5b3d41a76bf1f8ee9ee8a908f69973c533e","tid":325644,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:37:02.000Z","msg":"你自己on9答有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講下大話都唔識就抵你要車埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2f37b5376c1a0833b1208ee2d141ca8743f738","tid":325644,"uid":117747,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接答無位要去兜埋其他同事/朋友</blockquote><br />\n咦！呢招OK...下次攞嚟頂下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea00092202f167286f03d8210695f54437cd276e","tid":325644,"uid":117747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以後你都要車埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係諗緊以後連同事A都唔車...咁就唔洗煩！<br />\n不過同事A就會做咗炮灰...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462e34c496430efd830d52c8e5899c5949912785","tid":325644,"uid":117747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會直接唔車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢講有其他人要兜埋<br />\n擺到明唔妥你 吹咩<br />\n除非你要車既人同佢好熟/ 你要買佢怕</blockquote><br />\n同事A後尾話同佢都熟....所以真係諗緊唯有連同事A都唔車...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84586cae62af0c216e76c22322c2534381123e84","tid":325644,"uid":79877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會直接唔車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkg